des: Based on the hit game developed on the CAGCast, this is your opportunity to see how big of a Nintendo Switch fan you are! Can you tell the difference between AI generated Switch game names and the real ones? Challenge yourself across thousands of real and fake games, see if you can rack up the high score and best your friends!
